{"title":"Medallions","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"liberty-gold-coin","title":"Liberty Gold Coin","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"68\" data-end=\"89\"\u003eLiberty Gold Coin\u003c\/strong\u003e – A timeless collectible crafted to honor the spirit of freedom and American pride. Struck with exquisite detail, this coin is a symbol of strength, heritage, and lasting value — perfect for any patriot’s collection.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Our Maga Shop","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51277151338772,"sku":"0","price":199.99,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0967\/3775\/5412\/files\/H1b9ff8100f0f4fc7926b46092cc84d61y.jpg?v=1757598232"},{"product_id":"trump-1000-bitcoins-gold-bar","title":"Trump 1000 Bitcoins Gold Bar","description":"","brand":"Our Maga Shop","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51278102135060,"sku":"BTCBAR","price":19999.0,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0967\/3775\/5412\/files\/gempages_548339283191137160-ad70ef30-7bb3-44dc-b56e-498a9359e8c4.webp?v=1757617370"},{"product_id":"qfs-coin","title":"Golden QFS Coin | LIMITED EDITION","description":"\u003cp class=\"p1\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eGolden QFS Coin – Limited Edition \u003c\/b\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"p2\"\u003eCelebrate the new era with the Golden QFS Coin — a beautifully crafted collectible designed to inspire and symbolize prosperity. Plated in radiant gold with sharp detailing, this coin is made \u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eexclusively as memorabilia\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e and a timeless keepsake for collectors and patriots.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Our Maga Shop","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51315434815764,"sku":"QFSCOIN","price":1999.99,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0967\/3775\/5412\/files\/1764252873058-019ac5aa-10e0-7762-acdc-a5a96fc891ce-Photoroom.png?v=1764256193"},{"product_id":"nesara-gesara-qfs-gold-bar-1","title":"Nesara Gesara QFS Gold Bar","description":"\u003cp\u003eCrafted with a radiant gold finish and precision-engraved detailing, the \u003cstrong\u003eNESARA \/ GESARA QFS Gold Bar\u003c\/strong\u003e is far more than a collectible — it is a statement of belief, legacy, and unwavering patriotism.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEvery element of this piece reflects strength and purpose: from its refined craftsmanship to its certified presentation designed for those who recognize value beyond surface appearance. This gold bar symbolizes sovereignty, financial awakening, and the enduring spirit of individuals who stand for freedom and independence.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCreated for collectors who demand meaning, not mass production, this exclusive item represents faith in a brighter economic future and pride in American ideals. It is a timeless keepsake — bold, symbolic, and destined to be preserved as part of a legacy that transcends generations.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Our Maga Shop","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51859141525780,"sku":"QFSBAR","price":1999.99,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0967\/3775\/5412\/files\/QFSBARFRONTBACK.png?v=1768084851"},{"product_id":"qfs-coin-upsell","title":"QFS COIN – Upsell","description":"\u003cp class=\"p1\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eGolden QFS Coin – Limited Edition \u003c\/b\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"p2\"\u003eCelebrate the new era with the Golden QFS Coin — a beautifully crafted collectible designed to inspire and symbolize prosperity. Plated in radiant gold with sharp detailing, this coin is made \u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eexclusively as memorabilia\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e and a timeless keepsake for collectors and patriots.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Our Maga Shop","