first-2026-edition-silver-medallion","title":"President Trump First 2026 Edition Silver Medallion","description":"\u003cdiv data-id=\"gxZ5EfTNWo\" class=\"gxZ5EfTNWo\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"gp-flex\"\u003e\n\u003ch2 data-gp-text=\"\" class=\"gp-g-heading-1  gp-text-instant gp-text\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePremium, Patriotic, Built to Last:\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-id=\"gDK7RX8xWk\" class=\"gDK7RX8xWk\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"gp-flex\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-gp-text=\"\" class=\"gp-text-instant gp-text\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ecrafted with a polished silver finish and high-relief detailing for striking depth and clarity. each medallion is designed in america for americans, honoring the values that make our nation strong.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003elimited 2025 edition collectible\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003egleaming silver-plated finish\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ehigh-relief engraved design for vivid detail\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ediameter: 1.57\" (40mm)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eweight: approx. 1 oz\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eincludes protective acrylic capsule for display and preservation\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Our Maga Shop","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52247833968916,"sku":"TRSLVC","price":49.0,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0967\/3775\/5412\/files\/Untitled_design_-_2025-08-13T163525.187.webp?v=1773935791"}],"url":"https:\/\/ourmagashop.com\/collections\/medallions.oembed","provider":"Our Maga Shop","version":"1.0","type":"link"}